1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"How to create a WordPress Radionomy player\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player-tutorial/how-to-create-a-wordpress-radionomy-player/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 03 Mar 2018 01:31:52 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"WordPress Audio Player\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"WordPress Audio Player Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"WordPress Audio Player Tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=5696\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:447:\"Product: WonderPlugin Audio Player Tutorial: This tutorial will guide you how to create a WordPress Radionomy player with the plugin WonderPlugin Audio Player. Step 1: In WonderPlugin Audio Player, step 1, click the button \"Add Audio\", enter the Radionomy streaming &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player-tutorial/how-to-create-a-wordpress-radionomy-player/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1802:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Audio Player</a></p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p>This tutorial will guide you how to create a WordPress Radionomy player with the plugin WonderPlugin Audio Player.<br />\n<span id=\"more-5696\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong>:</p>\n<p>In WonderPlugin Audio Player, step 1, click the button \"Add Audio\", enter the Radionomy streaming URL to the \"Mp3 URL\" input box, check the option \"This is a live streaming\".</p>\n<p>If you would like to display the played track list, enter the radioUID of the Radionomy station.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player-600x446.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"446\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5699\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player-600x446.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player-240x178.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player-75x56.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player-404x300.png 404w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wordpress-radionomy-player.png 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong>:</p>\n<p>In the plugin, step 2, Skins tab, choose a skin from the skin list. If you would like to display the played track list, choose the skin \"White Box Live\" or \"Grey Box Live\". These two skins are created specifically for live streaming.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"How to manually install a WordPress plugin via FTP\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-manually-install-a-wordpress-plugin-via-ftp/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 22 Feb 2018 09:47:04 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=5649\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:403:\"This tutorial will guide you how to manually install a WordPress plugin ZIP file via FTP. Step 1: Extract the WordPress plugin ZIP file to a folder on your computer. Step 2: With your FTP software, upload the extracted Plugin &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-manually-install-a-wordpress-plugin-via-ftp/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1757:\"<p>This tutorial will guide you how to manually install a WordPress plugin ZIP file via FTP.<br />\n<span id=\"more-5649\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong>: Extract the WordPress plugin ZIP file to a folder on your computer.  </p>\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong>: With your FTP software, upload the extracted Plugin folder to the <code>wp-content/plugins</code> folder in your WordPress directory online. </p>\n<p>* <strong><em>When a ZIP file is extracted, some unzip software may add a parent folder outside of the Plugin folder. Please make sure you have uploaded the Plugin folder, not this parent folder.</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong>: Log into your WordPress backend, left menu, Plugins -> Installed Plugins, find the plugin from the list and click <code>Activate</code> to activate it.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin.png\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin-600x159.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"159\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5650\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin-600x159.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin-240x64.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin-768x203.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin-75x20.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin-500x132.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/wordpress-activate-plugin.png 876w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"Add pages created with Elementor to WordPress tabs\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:102:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tabs-plugin/add-pages-created-with-elementor-to-wordpress-tabs/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 21 Feb 2018 22:52:42 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress Tabs Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=5642\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:471:\"Product: WonderPlugin Tabs Question: Is the plugin WonderPlugin Tabs compatible with Elementor page builder https://en-au.wordpress.org/plugins/elementor/? I tried to add a page created with Elemantor to a tab, the content is loaded correctly, but all the design/styling is lost. Answer: You &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tabs-plugin/add-pages-created-with-elementor-to-wordpress-tabs/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1099:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tabs/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Tabs</a></p>\n<p><strong>Question</strong>:</p>\n<p>Is the plugin WonderPlugin Tabs compatible with Elementor page builder <a href=\"https://en-au.wordpress.org/plugins/elementor/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://en-au.wordpress.org/plugins/elementor/</a>?</p>\n<p>I tried to add a page created with Elemantor to a tab, the content is loaded correctly, but all the design/styling is lost.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-5642\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>:</p>\n<p>You can try the plugin <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/anywhere-elementor/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/anywhere-elementor/</a>.</p>\n<p>After you install the plugin, in WonderPlugin Tabs, step 1, click \"Add HTML Code\", then add the following shortcode to the HTML code.  </p>\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; title: ; notranslate\">\r\n[INSERT_ELEMENTOR id=XXXX]\r\n</pre>\n<p>Please make sure to change the XXXX to the ID of the page that was created with Elementor.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"How to manually install a WordPress plugin ZIP file\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:101:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-manually-install-a-wordpress-plugin-zip-file/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 08 Feb 2018 22:20:25 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=5629\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:403:\"This tutorial will guide you how to manually install a WordPress plugin ZIP file. Step 1: Log into your WordPress backend, on the left menu, click Plugins -> Add New, then click the button \"Upload Plugin\". Step 2: Select the &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-tutorials/how-to-manually-install-a-wordpress-plugin-zip-file/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4426:\"<p>This tutorial will guide you how to manually install a WordPress plugin ZIP file.<br />\n<span id=\"more-5629\"></span></p>\n<p>Step 1: Log into your WordPress backend, on the left menu, click Plugins -> Add New, then click the button \"Upload Plugin\".</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin-600x404.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"404\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5630\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin-600x404.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin-240x162.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin-768x518.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin-75x51.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin-445x300.png 445w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Upload-plugin.png 828w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Step 2: Select the WordPress plugin ZIP file and click the button Install Now.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file-600x322.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"322\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5631\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file-600x322.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file-240x129.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file-768x412.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file-75x40.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file-500x268.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/select-plugin-file.png 902w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Step 3: Activate the plugin after it\'s installed.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin-600x378.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5632\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin-600x378.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin-240x151.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin-75x47.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin-476x300.png 476w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activate-plugin.png 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If WordPress returns the following error:</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; title: ; notranslate\">\r\nDestination folder already exists. /www/wp-content/plugins/wonderplugin-carousel/\r\n\r\nPlugin installation failed.\r\n</pre>\n<p>It means the plugin (could be a previous version) is already installed. In this case, you need to deactivate and delete the existing version first.</p>\n<p>In the WordPress backend left menu, click Plugins -> Installed Plugins, find the plugin in the list. If the plugin is not activated, click the link <code>Delete</code> to remove the plugin. Otherwise, click <code>Deactivate</code> first, then click <code>Delete</code>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin.png\" class=\"wplightbox\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin-600x271.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5637\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin-600x271.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin-240x108.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin-768x346.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin-75x34.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin-500x226.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/delete-plugin.png 776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"Display PDF Transcript or Lyrics in WordPress Audio Player\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:117:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player-tutorial/display-pdf-transcript-lyrics-in-wordpress-audio-player/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 05 Jan 2018 22:53:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"WordPress Audio Player\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"WordPress Audio Player Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"WordPress Audio Player Tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=5571\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:411:\"Product: WonderPlugin Audio Player Version 6.1 or above Tutorial: This tutorial will guide you how to embed a PDF transcript or lyrics file with each audio file in the audio player. Step 1 - Add PDF URL to each audio &#8230; <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player-tutorial/display-pdf-transcript-lyrics-in-wordpress-audio-player/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WonderPlugin Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26737:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-audio-player/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Audio Player</a> Version 6.1 or above</p>\n<p><strong>Tutorial</strong>:</p>\n<p>This tutorial will guide you how to embed a PDF transcript or lyrics file with each audio file in the audio player.<br />\n<span id=\"more-5571\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong> - Add PDF URL to each audio file</p>\n<p>In the plugin, step 1, edit the audio file, enter the PDF URL to the Information input box.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf.png\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf-600x452.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"452\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5578\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf-600x452.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf-240x180.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf-75x57.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf-398x300.png 398w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-pdf.png 734w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong> - Customise the track list format to display the PDF file</p>\n<p>In the plugin, step 3 Options tab, Playlist, check the option \"Customise the playlist item format\", then enter the following text:</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; title: ; notranslate\">\r\n%ID%. %TITLE% &lt;span style=\'float:right;\'&gt;&lt;a href=\'%INFO%\' onclick=\'event.stopPropagation();\' target=\'_blank\'&gt;PDF&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist.png\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-600x157.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"157\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5598\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-600x157.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-240x63.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-768x201.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-1024x268.png 1024w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-75x20.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist-500x131.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-playlist.png 1158w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong> - Remove the information text from the player control area</p>\n<p>In the plugin, step 3 Options tab, Player Control, change the value of the input box \"Information format\" to the follows:</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; title: ; notranslate\">\r\n%ARTIST% %ALBUM%\r\n</pre>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat.png\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat-600x269.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"269\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5599\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat-600x269.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat-240x108.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat-768x344.png 768w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat-75x34.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat-500x224.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wordpress-audio-player-infoformat.png 832w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>An online demo is as follows:</p>\n<style type=\"text/css\">@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans);  #wonderpluginaudio-36 { 	box-sizing: content-box; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 div { 	-webkit-box-sizing: content-box; 	-moz-box-sizing: content-box; 	box-sizing: content-box;    }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-image { 	display: block; 	position: relative; 	float: left; 	margin: 4px; 	overflow: hidden; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-image img { 	display: inline-block; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 0; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-image-clear { }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-text { 	display: block; 	position: relative; 	text-align: left; 	overflow: hidden; 	padding: 8px; 	height: auto; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-text-clear { }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-title { 	display: block; 	color: #333; 	font-family: \"Open Sans\",Arial,sans-serif; 	font-size: 14px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-title-clear { }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-info { 	display: block; 	color: #666; 	font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, sans-serif; 	font-size: 12px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-info-clear { }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-bar { 	position: relative; 	width: auto; 	float: left; 	padding: 8px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-bar-buttons-clear { 	clear: both; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-bar-clear { 	clear: both; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-bar-title { 	position: relative; 	float: left; 	color: #eee; 	font-family: \"Open Sans\", sans-serif; 	font-size: 12px; 	line-height: 24px; 	margin: 0 8px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playpause { 	position: relative; 	float: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-play { 	position: relative; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-pause { 	position: relative; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-stop { 	position: relative; 	float: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-prev { 	position: relative; 	float: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-next { 	position: relative; 	float: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-loop { 	position: relative; 	float: left; 	margin: 0 2px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-progress { 	position: relative; 	background-color: #444; 	margin: 8px 4px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-progress-loaded { 	background-color: #666; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-progress-played { 	background-color: #fcc500; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-time { 	position: relative; 	float: right; 	color: #fff; 	font: bold 12px \"Open Sans\", sans-serif; 	margin: 8px; 	color: #333; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-volume { 	position: relative; 	float: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-volume-bar { 	background-color: #444; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-volume-bar-adjust { 	background-color: #333; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-volume-bar-adjust-active { 	background-color: #fcc500; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracklist { 	display: block; 	position: relative; 	background-color: #fff; 	padding: 4px; 	margin-top: 8px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracklist-container { 	display: block; 	position: relative; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracks-wrapper { 	position: relative; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracks { 	position: relative; 	list-style-type: none; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 0; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item { 	list-style-type: none; 	position: relative; 	cursor: pointer; 	color: #333; 	font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, sans-serif; 	font-size: 12px; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 8px 4px; 	text-align: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item-active { 	cursor: pointer; 	color: #333; 	background-color: #f0f0f0; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item a { 	color: #333; 	text-decoration: none; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item-active a { 	color: #333; 	text-decoration: none; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item-duration { 	position: absolute; 	top: 0; 	right: 0; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracklist-arrow-prev { 	position: absolute; 	bottom: 2px; 	left: 50%; 	margin-left: -64px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracklist-arrow-next { 	position: absolute; 	bottom: 2px; 	left: 50%; 	margin-left: 16px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-tracklist-clear { 	clear: both; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-item-id { 	float: left; 	width: 18px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-item-info { 	float: right; 	width: 36px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-item-title { 	overflow: hidden; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item:before, #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-track-item:after { 	display: none; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 ul, #wonderpluginaudio-36 li { 	list-style-type: none; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-player-wrapper { 	display: block; 	position: relative; 	background-color: #fff; 	padding: 4px; }   #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-wrapper { 	display: block; 	position: relative; 	background-color: #fff; 	padding: 0; 	margin-top: 8px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist { 	position: relative; 	list-style-type: none; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 4px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-title { 	font:14px \"Open Sans\",Arial,sans-serif; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 8px; 	color: #333; 	text-align: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item { 	list-style-type: none; 	position: relative; 	color: #333; 	font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, sans-serif; 	font-size: 12px; 	margin: 0; 	padding: 8px 4px; 	text-align: left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item:hover{ 	color: #333; 	background-color: #f0f0f0; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item-shoutcast-time {     font-size: 13px;     width: 90px;     display: block;     float:left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item-shoutcast-title {     display:block;     font-size:13px;     margin-left:90px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item-radionomy-image {     width: 60px;     display: block;     float:left; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item-radionomy-text {     display:block;     margin-left:60px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item-radionomy-title {     font-size: 13px;     margin: 4px;     padding: 0; }  #wonderpluginaudio-36 .amazingaudioplayer-playedlist-item-radionomy-artist {     font-size: 12px;     margin: 4px;     padding: 0; }</style><div class=\"wonderpluginaudio\" id=\"wonderpluginaudio-36\" data-audioplayerid=\"36\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"600\" data-skin=\"whitebox\" data-autoplay=\"false\" data-random=\"false\" data-forceflash=\"false\" data-forcehtml5=\"false\" data-autoresize=\"false\" data-responsive=\"false\" data-showtracklist=\"true\" data-tracklistscroll=\"true\" data-showprogress=\"true\" data-showprevnext=\"true\" data-showloop=\"true\" data-preloadaudio=\"true\" data-showtime=\"true\" data-showvolume=\"true\" data-showvolumebar=\"true\" data-showliveplayedlist=\"false\" data-showtitleinbar=\"false\" data-showloading=\"false\" data-enablega=\"true\" data-titleinbarscroll=\"true\" data-donotinit=\"false\" data-addinitscript=\"false\" data-loop=\"1\" data-tracklistitem=\"10\" data-titleinbarwidth=\"80\" data-gatrackingid=\"UA-47857964-1\" data-playpauseimage=\"playpause-36-36-0.png\" data-playpauseimagewidth=\"36\" data-playpauseimageheight=\"36\" data-prevnextimage=\"prevnext-36-36-0.png\" data-prevnextimagewidth=\"36\" data-prevnextimageheight=\"36\" data-volumeimage=\"volume-36-36-0.png\" data-volumeimagewidth=\"36\" data-volumeimageheight=\"36\" data-liveupdateinterval=\"10000\" data-maxplayedlist=\"8\" data-playedlisttitle=\"Last Tracks Played\" data-loopimage=\"loop-36-36-0.png\" data-loopimagewidth=\"36\" data-loopimageheight=\"36\" data-infoformat=\"%ARTIST% %ALBUM%\" data-tracklistitemformat=\"%ID%. %TITLE% <span style=\'float:right\'><a href=\'%INFO%\' onclick=\'event.stopPropagation();\' target=\'_blank\'>PDF</a></span>\" data-tracklistscroll=\"false\" data-jsfolder=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/plugins/wonderplugin-audio/engine/\" style=\"display:block;position:relative;margin:0 auto;width:300px;height:auto;\"><ul class=\"amazingaudioplayer-audios\" style=\"display:none;\"><li data-artist=\"pinkzebra\" data-title=\"In the Moment of Inspiration\" data-album=\"\" data-info=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/WordPress-Audio-Player.pdf\" data-image=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Evening100.jpg\" data-duration=\"154\"><div class=\"amazingaudioplayer-source\" data-src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/In-the-Moment-of-Inspiration.mp3\" data-type=\"audio/mpeg\" ></div><div class=\"amazingaudioplayer-source\" data-src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/In-the-Moment-of-Inspiration.ogg\" data-type=\"audio/ogg\" ></div></li><li data-artist=\"pinkzebra\" data-title=\"Peaceful Dawn\" data-album=\"\" data-info=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/WordPress-Lightbox.pdf\" data-image=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Island100.jpg\" data-duration=\"129\"><div class=\"amazingaudioplayer-source\" data-src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Peaceful-Dawn.mp3\" data-type=\"audio/mpeg\" ></div><div class=\"amazingaudioplayer-source\" data-src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Peaceful-Dawn.ogg\" data-type=\"audio/ogg\" ></div></li></ul></div>\n<p style=\"margin-top:36px;\">\n<p><strong>Open PDF files in a lightbox popup</strong></p>\n<p>With the help of the plugin <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-lightbox/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Lightbox</a>, you can also display the PDF files in a lightbox popup.</p>\n<p>Firstly, download and install the plugin <a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-lightbox/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WonderPlugin Lightbox</a>. </p>\n<p>After the plugin is installed and activated, in WonderPlugin Audio Player, step 3 Options tab, Playlist, change the playlist item format to:</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: xml; title: ; notranslate\">\r\n%ID%. %TITLE% &lt;span style=\'float:right\'&gt;&lt;a class=\'wplightbox\' data-width=\'1024\' data-height=\'960\' href=\'%INFO%\' onclick=\'event.stopPropagation();\' target=\'_blank\'&gt;PDF&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>To open the PDF file in a lightbox popup, the PDF file MUST be hosted on the SAME DOMAIN as your WordPress website. Please also make sure there are no special characters in the PDF URL, for example, apostrophes, double quotes, accented letters etc.</p>\n<p>An online demo is as follows:</p>\n<style type=\"text/css\">@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans|Raleway);  #wonderpluginaudio-37 { 	box-sizing: border-box; 	background-color: #333; 	border: 1px solid #222; 	-webkit-border-radius: 2px;     	-moz-border-radius: 2px;     	border-radius: 2px; 	margin: 4px; 	padding: 8px 4px; 	-webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba( 255, 255, 255, 0.15 ), 0 0 3px rgba( 0, 0, 0, 0.5 ); 	-moz-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba( 255, 255, 255, 0.15 ), 0 0 3px rgba( 0, 0, 0, 0.5 ); 	box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba( 255, 255, 255, 0.15 ), 0 0 3px rgba( 0, 0, 0, 0.5 ); 	background-image: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #444444 0%, #111111 100%); 	background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #444444 0%, #111111 100%); 	background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #444444 0%, #111111 100%); 	background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0, #444444), color-stop(1, #111111)); 	background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #444444 0%, #111111 100%); 	background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #444444 0%, #111111 100%); }  #wonderpluginaudio-37 div { 	-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; 	-moz-box-sizing: border-box; 	box-sizing: border-box;    }  #wonderpluginaudio-37 